Welcome to Pacific Blue Developments Ltd. We are Vancouver's premier custom home builders and we're here to make your dream a reality.  We specialize in custom homes, lane way homes, and duplexes.  Our experience, and knowledge of construction allows us to take the hassle out of building. We'll set a time to sit down with you and go over your project needs and work with you to achieve them. 

Some special things about us:

-We are family owned business
-We are a locally owned and operated business 
-We work on residential projects
-We work on commercial projects 
-We do all types of renovations 
-We work on and build high end homes 
-We work on and build cookie cutter homes 


****

Contact us today to schedule an appointment. We're looking forward to working with you.

profile:
WE BUILD HOMES, NOT HOUSES.
Buying or building your dream home is one of the biggest and most important purchases you will ever make.  At Icon, we know this and strive to make your experience as pleasant as possible.

OUR PHILOSOPHY.
Passion, drive, and dedication.  Our ultimate goal is to create homes that are built to superior standards with striking architectural form without sacrificing function. Through precise planning and exacting execution, our homes are built to last a lifetime while staying on time and on budget.

PEOPLE, NOT CORPORATIONS.
Working with us means that you will really be working with us!  No intermediaries and no gatekeepers.  Your project manager will provide you with regular schedule updates and construction site photos via email so you always know what is going on.  You will be able to reach your site superintendant at anytime via cell phone or email.

profile:
At Terry Custom Homes we take pride in developing good relationships, hearing and implementing our customers’ needs and desires. My satisfaction comes from your appreciation at the end of a well done project.
We always make a contract stating explicitly the scope of work to be done, how much it will cost and a time for completion.
We build custom homes and renovations in the Greater Fraser Valley of all sizes and types; from ranchers, to two-storey with basement, mountainside, energy efficient, regular foundations, raft foundations, ICF foundations and Timber frame.
My background began in 1973 building a summer cottage, this progressed into my own framing business and then into custom home building and renovations including office renovations. In 1993 I earned the designation of R-2000 Home builder and in 1994 the Certified Residential Builder designation. I personally spend a lot of supervision time at the job ensuring the highest quality. We have great trades that are focused on doing it right the first time.
It is our desire to make your dream a reality.
So when looking for a Homebuilder, General contractor, Renovator or Kitchen, Bathroom planner please check us out.
